   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"Panechotes, foreman of the . . . . . . in Ibion Panektyreos to Matreas, the most honored, greetings. If it seems good to you, give instructions for the payment of the expenses I have incurred, for which I shall render an account, three hundred silver drachmas, total 300 silver drachmas. Year 20 of the Emperor Caesar Titus Aelius Hadrianus Antoninus Augustus Pius, the 25th Epeiph. (2nd hd.) Give only 200 drachmas."</ab>
         </div>
